      *
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN88
     C                     Z-ADDD@DATE    K@YMD
     C           K#KEY     SETLLAB#PL75
     C           *IN80     DOUEQ*ON
     C           K#KEY     READEAB#PL75                  80
     C           *IN80     IFEQ *OFF
JW   C           PUSKJY    ANDNE'D'
